collectionMetadata.name: Top 10 Conditions of Hospitalisation
collectionMetadata.description:
Top 10 conditions of hospitalization

Notes:

1.  The ranking of disease conditions would exclude ill-defined conditions and non-disease entities such as legally induced abortion, normal and assisted delivery, prematurity, physiological jaundice in the newborn, and contact with health services  

2.  The Tabulation List of the International Classification of Diseases - Tenth Revision (ICD10AM) has replaced the Ninth Revision as the adopted code set for the derivation of causes of hospitalisation wef Year 2012.

3. For data prior to Year 2012, refer to Download.
